<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>阿马尔菲海岸终极旅行指南</title>
  <style>
    :root {
      --blue: #2a5f8a;
      --green: #6b8e23;
      --gold: #d4a017;
      --text: #333;
      --bg: #f9f9f9;
    }
    body {
      font-family: 'Noto Sans SC', 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.8;
      color: var(--text);
      background: var(--bg);
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 0 20px;
    }
    header {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 4rem 0;
      background: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.4), rgba(0,0,0,0.4)), 
                  url('./images/01.jpg') center/cover;
      color: white;
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
      border-radius: 0 0 20px 20px;
    }
    h1 {
      font-size: 2.8rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      text-shadow: 2px 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.6);
    }
    .destination-card {
      background: white;
      border-radius: 12px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
      margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    }
    .destination-image {
      width: 100%;
      height: 380px;
      object-fit: cover;
      border-bottom: 4px solid var(--gold);
    }
    .destination-content {
      padding: 1.8rem;
    }
    .highlight-tag {
      background: var(--gold);
      color: white;
      padding: 6px 12px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      display: inline-block;
      margin: 0.3rem;
    }
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      h1 { font-size: 2.2rem; }
      .destination-image { height: 280px; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <h1>阿马尔菲海岸终极旅行指南</h1>
    <p>探索地中海岸的宝石：从波西塔诺到拉韦洛</p>
  </header>

  <main>
    <!-- 波西塔诺 -->
    <article class="destination-card">
      <img src="./images/01.jpg" 
           alt="波西塔诺"
           class="destination-image" 
           loading="lazy"
           width="800" 
           height="450">
      <div class="destination-content">
        <h2>波西塔诺</h2>
        <p>意大利最著名的悬崖小镇，彩色房屋如瀑布般倾泻至地中海，拥有绝美的沙滩和奢侈品商店。</p>
        <div>
          <span class="highlight-tag">斯皮亚格亚海滩</span>
          <span class="highlight-tag">圣母升天教堂</span>
          <span class="highlight-tag">Path of the Gods徒步</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>

    <!-- 阿马尔菲镇 -->
    <article class="destination-card">
      <img src="./images/02.jpg" 
           alt="阿马尔菲镇"
           class="destination-image" 
           loading="lazy"
           width="800" 
           height="450">
      <div class="destination-content">
        <h2>阿马尔菲镇</h2>
        <p>历史上强大的海上共和国，以其宏伟的大教堂和手工造纸闻名。</p>
        <div>
          <span class="highlight-tag">圣安德烈大教堂</span>
          <span class="highlight-tag">手工造纸博物馆</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>

    <!-- 拉韦洛 -->
    <article class="destination-card">
      <img src="./images/03.jpg" 
           alt="拉韦洛"
           class="destination-image" 
           loading="lazy"
           width="800" 
           height="450">
      <div class="destination-content">
        <h2>拉韦洛</h2>
        <p>艺术家偏爱的山顶桃源，鲁菲洛别墅的花园是《十日谈》的灵感来源。</p>
        <div>
          <span class="highlight-tag">辛波乃别墅</span>
          <span class="highlight-tag">瓦格纳音乐节</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>
  </main>

  <footer style="text-align: center; padding: 2rem; color: var(--blue);">
    <p>© <span id="year"></span> 阿马尔菲海岸旅行指南</p>
  </footer>

  <script>
    // 自动更新年份
    document.getElementById('year').textContent = new Date().getFullYear();
  </script>
</body>
</html>
